Version 0.11
============
* add a user manual
* add svg and 48x48 icons, use them in notifications
* add DBus API to destroy ticket cache (can be used by e.g. on laptop suspend,
  screensaver, ...)
* cleanups and bug fixes
* i18n updates:
	* de: Guido Günther
	* es: Jorge Gonzalez
